original_title: Sith Wars: Episódio II - O Legado Dos Sith
overview: After the defeat at Agamar, Darth Vader discovers that both Master Yoda and Master Vaal, are training a new apprentice who is rumored to be able to defeat the sith, now he takes a personal vendetta against the rest of the Jedi order.
tagline: The Secrets Of The Sith Will Be Revealed...
title: Sith Wars Ep II - The Legacy Of The Sith
